\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\series bold
Efficiency
\series default
: the institutional framework (market economy vs, regulation), trade and
 mobility restrictions, monopolies, financial system and government functioning
 and many more differences that can explain why some countries are able
 to produce more, given the same resources.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\series bold
Institutions, culture and policy 
\series default
influence efficiency the most (property protection rights - from each other
 and from the state, trust - a very important thing for economic growth).
\end_layout

